>\n鱷魚裇咪又要改logo ，仲要做埋lacoste 代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86ea74ac35aaee51859df0a348d9f3656b7c9d9","tid":499654,"uid":47674,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>類似情況<br />\n當年lacoste同鱷魚恤又傾得掂數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鱷魚裇咪又要改logo ，仲要做埋lacoste 代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n支那就抄人logo唔肯改仲要罰人一大筆錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd188f8b3f8baa1aa6ba7fce9d8369b963a314a","tid":499654,"uid":66991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:33:03.000Z","msg":"蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"80f2ae6a12106a7a144e2ac226a5d53537726bd5","tid":499654,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:38:05.000Z","msg":"抵啦成班白皮豬為左支那個市場寧願俾人踏到上心口都唔敢嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f557ff93c0854cb728079e8f09a87c23bc0443e","tid":499654,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"咁都告得入<br />\n<br />\n李寧牌咪執得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://blog.ulifestyle.com.hk/blogger/ilikegag/wp-content/blogs.dir/0/2583/files/2015/11/nike_01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fblogger%2Filikegag%2Fwp-content%2Fblogs.dir%2F0%2F2583%2Ffiles%2F2015%2F11%2Fnike_01.png&h=6fd095ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"daa2a47da5fc261db3b196241bcabe794b